keyMappings:
unmap J
unmap K
unmap H
unmap L
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-i> goForward
map <c-o> goBack
map J goForward
map K goBack
map <c-p> togglePinTab
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map D$ closeTabsOnRight
map D^ closeTabsOnLeft
unmap ^
map <c-6> visitPreviousTab
searchEngines:
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s YouTube
z: https://www.zhihu.com/search?type=content&q=%s Zhihu
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
a: https://arxiv.org/search/?searchtype=all&source=header&query=%s Arxiv
gs: https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=%s Google Scholar
d: https://dict.youdao.com/result?word=%s&lang=en Dict
